Class ScopedDefinitionTraitsVisitor

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITraitsVisitor, IVisitor

    public class ScopedDefinitionTraitsVisitor
extends Object
implements ITraitsVisitor
    This ITraitsVisitor creates definition for each trait, and add the definitions to a scope object.
